Usizo lwesikhashana  
ukuhlinzekwa kwanoma iyiphi indawo yokuhlala noma okokuziphilisa ; 
noma yokucela lowo muntu ukuba enze umnikelo wanoma iluphi uhlobo nganoma isiphi isizathu ; 
noma umuntu noma inhlangano ehlinzeka ngamasevisi okudala uxolo , ukubuyisana , nokulamula ukuze isize ekuxazululeni izingaxabano zabathengi , engeyena ummeleli osemthethweni onelungelo elingokomthetho lokukhipha izinqumo , noma ummeleli osemthethwei wezezimboni ogunyaziwe ; 
elithi iKhabhinethi lisho indikimba yabaphathi bakazwelonke abachazwe esigabani 91 soMthetho-Sisekelo ; 
yikuphi ukungcebeleka noma into ethile engaphatheki ngesandla noma ukutholakala kwanoma yikuphi ukungcebeleka okunjalo noma umkhiqizo ongaphatheki ngesandla ; 
noma ulawulwa ngokwemibandela yoMthetho Womshuwalesi Wesikhathi Eside , ka-1998 , noma uMthetho Womshuwalensi Wesikhashana , ka-1998 ; 
elithi umseshi lisho umuntu obekwe ukuba abe ngumseshi ngokuhambisana nemibandela yesigaba 88 ; 
elithi ukuqashisa lisho isivumelwano sokukhokha ekuqhutshweni kwebhizinisi okuvamile , ngokuvumelana nemibandela yokuhlinzekwa kwesikhashana kwendawo noma isakhiwo ngokuqondisa komthengi , noma ilungelo lokusebenzisa noma iyiphi indawo noma esinye isakhiwo kunikezwa othile noma ngesiqondiso somthengi , kodwa akuhlanganisi isivumelwano ngaphakathi kwencazelo yoMthetho Wezikweletu Kazwelonke ; 
noma ugunyazwe ngomunye umuntu ukuba akwazi ukuthola izinto ezithile ezisebenzisakayo noma ukusebenzisa noma yiziphi izimpahla ; 
Umphumela wophenyo  
elithi phakela , lapho lisetshenziswa nebizo ngokuhlobene nezimpahla , lihlanganisa ukuthengisa , ukuqashisa , ukushintshanisa , ukuqasha , nokuthengisa ngesitolimenti ekuqhutshweni okuvamile kwebhizinisi ukuze kutholwe inkokhelo ; 
elithi olanda izimpahla kwamanye amazwe maqondana nanoma yiziphi izimpahla , lisho umuntu oletha lezo zimpahla , noma obangela ukuba zilethwe , zisuka ngaphandle kweRiphabhuliki zingene kwiRiphabhuliki , ngenhloso yokuzenza zitholakale ngenjongo yokuthengiswa ngendlela evamile yokuqhutshwa kwebhizinisi ; 
noma ukutholakala noma ukuvunyelwa ukusebenzisa noma yiziphi izakhiwo noma indawo ngokuvumelana nemibandela yokuqasha ilungelo lokuba ngumhlali , noma igunya noma amandla okuhlala kunoma yiliphi izwe noma empahleni engathutheki , ngokungafani nemibandela yokuqashiswa ; 
noma ukuba khona , isimo , ukutholakala , izimpahla , izinzuzo noma ukusetshenziswa kwanoma iziphi izimpahla noma amasevisi atholakalayo ukuze aphakelwe abathengi , noma imibandela , noma amanani ahambisana nanoma iziphi izimpahla ezitholakalayo ngenjongo yokuphakelwa kwabathengi . 
elithi inani lapho lisetshenziswa maqondana nalokho okudingekayo okumelwe kuboniswe yisigaba 23 , libandakanya noma yiluphi uphawu , isaziso noma lokho okubonakala ngamehlo okungase kusikisele ukubonisa noma ukuveza ukuhlobana phakathi kwanoma yiziphi izimpahla noma amasevisi kanye nenani elicatshangelwayo umphakeli azimisele ukuthengisa noma ukuphakela ngalo lezo zimpahla noma amasevisi ; 
elithi umgudu wabaphakeli , ngokuqondene nanoma yiziphi izimpahla noma amasevisi , lisho ukuhlanganiswa ndawonye kwabo bonke abaphakeli , ngokuqondile noma ngenye indlela ababambe iqhaza ekuphakelweni kwalezo zimpahla noma amasevisi kumthengi , kungakhathaliseki ukuthi bangabakhiqizi noma abathenga kwamanye amazwe , abasakaza izimpahla kwabanye noma abazithengisayo , noma abangabahlinzeki bamasevisi ; 
elithi umthetho kahulumeni lisho isishayamthetho noma isishayamthetho esingaphansi sikazwelonke , sesifundazwe noma sikahulumeni wasekhaya , noma nanoma iyiphi ilayisensi , uhlu olusemthethweni lwemisebenzi kahulumeni , isiqondiso noma igunya elifanayo elikhishwa igunya elilawulayo noma okuvumelana nanoma yiliphi igunya elilawulayo ; 
noma ukubandakanyeka kunoma yiluphi olunye uhlobo lokuziphatha ekuqhutshweni kwebhizinisi okuvamile okungase kuchazwe njengesisusa/imbangela noma isisusa esihlosiwe kumuntu sokubandakanyeka ekuqhutshweni kwebhizinisi ; 
elithi lo Mthetho lihlanganisa noma yiluphi uHlelo kulo Mthetho , iziqondiso ezibekiwe noma isaziso esikhishwe nguNgqongqoshe ngaphansi kwalo Mthetho ; kanti elithi okubonakala emehlweni lisho noma yini ebonisiwe noma ekhangisiwe engabuye ikhiqizwe , kungakhathaliseki ukuthi ikhiqizwa ngokuphrintwa noma ngezinye izindlela , kodwa alihlanganisi uphawu lokuhweba . 
elithi umphakeli lisho umuntu othengisa nganoma yiziphi izimpahla noma amasevisi ; 
elithi umphakeli , maqondana nanoma iziphi izimpahla , usho umuntu ekuqhutshweni kwebhizinisi elivamile ophakelwa lezo zimpahla ngumkhiqizi wazo , ozilanda kwamanye amazwe noma omunye umphakeli ; 
ukutholakala kwanoma iyiphi ingqalasizinda yezokuxhumana ngobuchwepheshe besimanje ; 
elithi igunya lokuvikelwa kwabathengi lasesifundazweni lisho indikimba emiswe ngaphakathi kukahulumeni wesifundazwe , futhi ebekwe yilungu eliqondisayo loMkhandlu Ophethe wesifundazwe ukuba ibe negunya lokusingatha izindaba zokuvikelwa kwabathengi kuleso sifundazwe ; 
kanye nanoma isiphi isiqondiso esinomphumela omuhle owenza ngcono , ovikela , ukhuthaze futhi uqinisekise ukuqashelwa kwamalungelo ngabathengi ngokwemibandela yalo Mthetho . 
isivumelwano sokuqhuba ibhizinisi le-franchise noma isivumelwano esiphelelisa isivumelwano sokwenza i-franchise . 
Lo Mthetho awusebenzi kunoma yikuphi ukuthengiselana ngokwemibandela izimpahla noma amasevisi akhangiswa ngayo eMbusweni , noma ahlinzekwa ngayo ngokuqondisa koMbuso ; 
Lo Mthetho kumelwe uchazwe ngendlela eyenza zigcizeleleke izinjongo ezivezwe esigabeni 3 . 
Lapho echaza noma esebenzisa lo Mthetho , umuntu , inkantolo , noma iNkantolo Yobulungisa noma uKhomishane angase acabangele umthetho ofanelekayo wakwamanye amazwe noma womhlaba wonke ; 
futhi izimpahla noma amasevisi kuphakelwa umuntu ngomgudu wokuphakela , okuthi ekuqhutshweni kwebhizinisi okuvamile athenge lezo zimpahla ukuze azithengise futhi , kungakhathaliseki ukuthi kwabanye abantu ngomgudu wokuphakela noma kubathengi gokuqondile ; 
UNgqongqoshe angase abhale phansi ngokusemthethweni ukwaziswa okumelwe kufakwe ezivumelwaneni ze-franchise , kabanzi , noma ngaphakathi kwezigaba noma izimboni ezithile . 
ukuqapha nokubika kuNgqongqoshe unyaka ngamunye ngalezi zindaba ezilandelayo : 
Umuntu obamelele umuntu ogunyaziwe omelele omunye umuntu ongeke akwazi ukwenza lutho egameni labo ; 
ukuphakelwa kwanoma yiziphi izimpahla noma amasevisi kwi-franchise ngokwemibandela yesivumelwano se-franchise Naphezu kwesigatshana , lo Mthetho usebenza ekuqhutshweni kwebhizinisi okuchazwe engxenyaneni ukuya ku- kungakhathaliseki kuthi inani imali yalokho kuqhutshwa kwebhizinisi iba ngaphezu noma ngaphansi kwesilinganiso esinqunyiwe ngokwemibandela yesigaba 6 . 
futhi kuhambisane nezimfuneko zesigaba 22 . 
kanye nenhlangano esebenzela izithakazelo zamalungu ayo . 
abangabantwana , abangabantu abadala noma abanye abathengi abayizisulu ezifanayo ; 
Naphezu kwezikhathi ezibekwe esigabeni 6 , umgaqo ngamunye ngokulandelana kwayo onqunywa nguNgqongqoshe ngokwemibandela yaleyo ngxenye uyaqhubeka usebenza kuze kube yilapho umgaqo olandelayo ngokwemibandela yaleyo ngxenye uqala ukusebenza . 
noma isivumelwano , umthetho womhlaba wonke , noma iphrothokholi . 
futhi ngokuvumelana nanoma yimiphi imingcele noma imibandela edingekile ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukufinyelelwa kwezinjongo zalo Mthetho . 
Uma kukhona ukungavumelani phakathi kwanoma yikuphi ukuhlinzekwa kwalo Mthetho , nokuhlinzekwa kwanoma yimuphi omunye uMthetho okungachaziwe engxenyaneni  ukuhlinzekwa kwayo yomibili le Mithetho kusebenza kanye kanye , ngokwezinga okungenzeka kusebenze ngalo futhi kuvumelane nenye yezinhlinzeko ezingavumelani ngaphandle kokungqubuzana neyesibili ; 
noma asebenzise lezo zimpahla noma lawo masevisi ekukhiqizweni kwezinye izimpahla noma amasevisi , noma ekuthengisweni kwanoma yiziphi ezinye izimpahla noma amasevisi , kungakhathaliseki ukuthi kwabanye abantu ngomgudu wokuphakela noma kubathengi ngokuqondile ; 
Kunoma yikuphi ukusebenzelana nomthengi noma ongaba ngumthengi lapho kuqhutshwa ibhizinisi , umuntu akumelwe abandakanyeke kunoma yikuphi ukuziphatha okungqubuzana noma okubhekwa njengokuyokhungathekisa noma kuphikisane nezinjongo nenqubomgomo yalo Mthetho ; 
noma kudingeka noma kukhishwe ilayisensi ngokwemibandela yanoma yimuphi umthetho kahulumeni wokuphakelwa kwezimpahla noma amasevisi athile atholakala kubo bonke noma engxenyeni ethile yomphakathi . 
ukukhuthaza ukuzethemba , ukufukulwa , kanye nokwakha impucuko yokukhathalela kubathengi , ngemfundo enikezwa abantu ngabanye noma amaqembu , ukuqapha , ukusekelana nokukhankasela amalungelo . 
Injongo nenqubomgomo yalo Mthetho  
sihlanganise noma yikuphi ukwaziswa okubhalwe ngokusemthethweni , noma kubhekele noma yiziphi izigaba zokwaziswa ezibhalwe ngokusemthethweni ; 
nangokukhipha noma yiliphi iholide lomphakathi , uMgqibelo noma iSonto eliwela ezinsukwini noma phakathi kwezinsuku ezichazwe ezindimeni no- ngokulandelana . 
Incazelo  
Kunoma yiluphi udaba olulethwe phambi kweNkantolo Yobulungisa noma iNkantolo ngokwemibandela yalo Mthetho Inkantolo kumelwe yakhe umthetho osebenzayo kuye ngesidingo ukuze kuthuthukiswe ukutholakala nokujatshulelwa kwamalungelo abathengi wonkana , futhi ikakhulukazi ngabantu abachazwe esigabeni 3 ; 
noma enze ukukhulumela nganoma yimuphi umphakeli noma izimpahla noma amasevisi , noma udaba oluhlobene nalokhu , ngale kokuba umuntu enezizathu ezizwakalayo zokukholelwa ukuthi lokho kukhulumela kuyiqiniso . 
kanye nokwenza ucwaningo , nokuhlongoza izinqubomgomo kuNgqongqoshe ngokuphathelene nanoma yiluphi olunye udaba oluthinta ukuphakelwa kwezimpahla namasevisi , kuhlanganisa ukuhlongozwa kwesishayamthetho , izinqubo zokuqondisa noma zenkambiso ezothuthukisa ukutholakala nokujatshulelwa kwamalungelo abathengi babo ngabantu abachazwe engxenyaneni . 
Ngokuqinisekile , amalungiselelo alandelayo kumelwe abhekwe njengokusebenzelana phakathi komphakeli nomthengi , ngaphakathi kwencazelo yalo Mthetho Ukuphakelwa kwanoma yiziphi izimpahla noma amasevisi ekuqhutshweni kwebhizinisi okuvamile kunoma yiliphi lamalungu ayo ngeqembu , ngenyonyana yezohwebo , ngenhlangano , ngesosayathi , noma ngomgwamanda othile , kungakhathaliseki ukuthi uyinkampani noma awuhleliwe waba yinkampani , wabantu abahlangene ngokuzithandela ngenjongo noma ngezinjongo ezifanayo , ngamanani okuvunyelwane ngawo noma ngenye indlela ehlukile , kungakhathaliseki ukuthi kunemali ekhokhiswayo noma imali ethile engokomnotho efunwayo noma elindelekile ukuze umuntu abe yilungu noma ahlale eyilungu laleyo nhlangano . 
noma uma ukuthengiselana/ukusebenzelana kungena ngaphansi kohlu lwezinto uNgqongqoshe azikhululile kulo Mthetho ngokwemibandela yezisigatshana no-Igunya eliphethe lingase lifake isicelo kuNgqongqoshe sokukhululwa embonini kabanzi ohlinzekweni olulodwa noma ezengeziwe zalo Mthetho ngezizathu zokuthi lezo zinhlinzeko ziyalekenyana noma ziphindaphinda uhlelo lokuphatha olukhishwe yilelo gunya eliphethe ngokwemibandela yanoma yisiphi esinye isishayamthetho sikazwelonke ; Ukunquma isilinganiso   
umuntu osebenzela izithakazelo zomphakathi , ngemvume yeNkantolo Yobulungisa noma yeNkantolo , ngokuvumelana nokunqunyiwe ; 
kanye nanoma yiluphi olunye udaba oluphathelene nokuphakelwa kwezimpahla namasevisi ; 
Ungqongqoshe , ngokusebenzisa isaziso ku-Somqulu , ngemva kokuthola ukucetshiswa nguKhomishane , angase avumele ukukhululwa emthethweni okuchazwe engxenyaneni  kuphela kuze kube sezingeni lapho okungenani uhlelo oluphethe olufanelekile luqinisekisa khona ukufinyelelwa kwezinjongo zalo Mthetho kanye nokuhlinzekwa kwalo Mthetho ; 
kanye nanoma yisiphi isinqumo senkantolo yabathengi , ummeleli osemthethweni noma umxazululi wezingxabano ngokwemibandela yalo mthetho , kuze kube sezingeni lapho lesi sinqumo singazange sibekelwe eceleni noma sihlehliswe noma senqatshwe yiNkantolo Ephakeme , iNkantolo Enkulu Yokudluliswa Kwamacala , noma iNkantolo Yomthetho-Sisekelo . 
Lapho kunikezwa inani elithile lezinsuku zebhizinisi phakathi kwesenzakalo sento ethile nesinye isenzakalo sento ethile , inani lezinsuku kumelwe libalwe  ngokukhipha usuku okwenzeka ngalo leso senzakalo sokuqala ngokubala usuku isenzakalo sesibili esizokwenzeka ngalo ; 
INkantolo noma iNkantolo Yobulungisa , kuye ngokuthi iyiphi , kumelwe ikhuthaze umuzwa nezinjongo zalo Mthetho ; 
abakhono labo lokufunda nokuqonda noma isiphi isikhangiso , isivumelwano , uphawu , isiyalezo , ilebula , isixwayiso , isaziso nanoma yini enye ebonakala ngamehlo lilinganiselwe ngenxa yokungabi namfundo , ukungaboni emehlweni , noma ukungaluqondi kahle ulimi umkhiqizo okhishwe , washicilelwa noma wethulwa ngalo ; 
ukutholakala kwezimpahla namasevisi ngamabhizinisi amancane kanye nabantu abachazwe engxenyaneni ; 
Othole ilungelo lokuthengisa impahla angase asisule isivumelwano sokuqhuba i-franchise ngaphandle kokukhokhiswa noma inhlawulo phakathi nezinsuku ezingu-10 zokusebenza ngemva kokusayina leso sivumelwano , ngokunikeza isaziso esilotshiwe kumhlinzeki welungelo lokuthengisa impahla . 
ukukhangiswa kwanoma yiziphi izimpahla noma amasevisi , noma zomphakeli wanoma yiziphi izimpahla noma amasevisi , ngaphakathi kwiRiphabhuliki , ngaphandle uma lezo zimpahla noma lawo masevisi eyisizathu esiyinhloko sokuthengiselana lo Mthetho obhekisela kuso ngokwemibandela yendima ; 
