Ukudluliselwa eNkantolo Yobulungisa  
Ngemva kokuthola umbiko wokuphenya ngesikhalazo , uKhomishane angase akhiphe isaziso sokuluhoxisa uphenyo kowenze isikhalazo ngokubhala phansi ; 
ethule isikhalazo kwelinye inxusa lokuxazululwa kwezingxabano , igunya lokuvikelwa kwamalungelo abathengi lasesifundazweni , noma inkantolo yabatheng ngezinjongo zokusiza abathintekayo ukuba bazame ukuxazulula ingxabano ngokwemibandela yesigaba 70 , ngale kokuba abathintekayo beye bazama esikhathini esidlule ukuxazulula ingxabano kodwa kwanhlanga zimuka nomoya ; 
Lesi sigaba asisebenzi kunoma yiluphi uketshezi , izingxenye noma izakhi ezidingekayo ngokwemibandela yanoma iyiphi iwaranti umsebenzi owenziwa ngaphansi kwayo , okuzofuneka ibuyiselwe kumkhiqizi noma umthengisi , noma ezolahlwa ngesiqondiso sakhe ; 
Uma uKhomishane enezizathu ezizwakalayo zokukholelwa ukuthi izimpahla kungenzeka aziphephile , noma ukuthi kukhona ingozi esina ijeqeza umphakathi ngokuqhubeka zisetshenziswa nokuchayeka kulezo zimpahla , futhi umkhiqizi noma ozilande kwamanye amazwe engazange athathe zinyathelo ezidingekayo ezifunwa ngumthetho osebenzayo ochazwe esigatshaneni , uKhomishane , ngesaziso esibhalwe phansi , angase afune ukuba umkhiqizi enze uphenyo oluchazwe esigatshanen ; 
azise abathengi ngesimo , izimbangela , ubungako nezinga lezingozi eziphathelene nalezo zimpahla ; 
Uma udaba luye lwaphenywa nguKhomishane , futhi uKhomishane nommangelelwa bevumelana nemibandela ehlongozwayo yesinqumo esifanelekile , iNkantolo yobulungisa noma inkantolo , ngaphandle kokuzwa noma yibuphi ubufakazi , ingase iqinisekise leso sivumelwano njengesinqumo sokuvuma . 
futhi zingakedluli izinsuku ezinhlanu zomsebenzi ngemva kokuvala leyo ndawo ; 
UKhomishane angase ngokuqondile noma ngenye indlela ethule isikhalazo maqondana nanoma yikuphi ukuziphatha okuye kwamangalelwa njengokunqatshenwe ngokubona kwakhe , noma lapho eqondiswa ukuba enze kanjalo kuNgqongqoshe ngokwemibandela yyesigaba 86 ; 
UKhomishane kumelwe akhuthaze , phakathi nohlaka lwesigaba 82 , ukuthuthukiswa , ukwamukelwa nokusetshenziswa kwemithetho yezimboni kabanzi yokusebenza enikeza izinhlelo eziphumelelayo nezilula ukuze amukele isaziso- sezikhalazo zomthengi noma imibiko yokwehluleka komkhiqizo , izimfa nezingozi ; sokulimala komuntu siqu , ukugula noma ukulimala kwempahla okubangelwe ngokuphelele noma ngokwengxenye ukwehluleka komkhiqizo , imfa noma ingozi ;  
noma ukufaka isikhalazo kuKhomishane ngokuvumelana nengxenye 71 ; noma uma umphakeli engekho ngaphansi kommeleli wezezimboni olwa nenkohlakalo ochazwe endimaneni  ukufaka isicelo enkantolo yabathengi yesifundazwe okuyiyona egunyazwe ukusingatha lolu daba , uma ikhona inkantolo enjalo yabathengi , kuye ngomthetho ophethe noma olawula leyo nkantolo yabathengi ukuqondisa lolo daba kwelinye inxusa lokuxazululwa kwezingxabano elichazwe esigabeni 70 ;  
noma yikuphi ukulahlekelwa , noma ukulila kwangempela kwanoma iyiphi impahla , kungakhathaliseki ukuthi iyathutheka noma ayithutheki ; 
Uma umuntu ebuyisa ibhodlela , into yokuphatha , iphalethi , irili , noma enye into efanayo echazwe esigatshaneni kunoma yimuphi umphakeli wezimpahla ezathengiswa zikulelo bhodlela noma leyo nto yokuphatha noma zikuleyo phalethi noma kuleyo rili noma enye into efanayo , umphakeli kumelwe akhokhele lowo muntu imali yediphozi uma noma yini okudingeka ukuba ikhokhiswe ngokwemibandela yanoma yimuphi umthetho kahulumeni ngosuku leyo nto ebuyiswa ngalo kumphakeli ; 
noma kudalwe ngokuphelele ukuhambisana nomthetho kwalowo muntu onikezwe iziyalezo ngumuntu ophakele lezo zimpahla kulowo muntu , ngaleyo ndlela indimana ayisebenzi ; 
futhi aqinisekise ukuthi leyo mali noma impahla iyabhekelwa ngokwenzuzo yomthengi ngokuvumelana nalesi sigaba ; 
Ezimweni ezichazwe esigatshaneni , uKhomishane angase ethule lolu daba enkantolo yabathengi yesifundazwe lapho umthengi enendawo eyinhloko yebhizinisi khona kwiRiphabhuliki , uma- ikhona inkantolo yabathengi kuleso sifundazwe ; 
