Uma umphakeli ehlose ukuvala indawo umphakeli abenesibopho sokuvumela ukuba kungenwe kuyo esikhathini esizayo ngokwemibandela yesivumelwano nomthengi sokuhlinzeka nganoma iyiphi isevisi , ngaphandle kokuba enze kube nenye indawo okungase kuyiwe kuyo , umphakeli kumelwe anikeze isaziso esilotshiwe saleyo nhloso kulowo mthengi okungenani kusasele izinsuku zomsebenzi ezingu-40 ngaphambi kosuku lokuvala oluhlosiwe ; 
Uma ummeleli wezezimboni olwa nenkohlakalo ochazwe esigatshaneni ephetha ngokuthi kubonakala kungenakwenzeka ukuba abahilelekile baxazulule ingxabano yabo ngenqubo ehlinzekiwe ngomthetho ofanelekayo wezezimboni inxusa lingase liyinqamule lenqubo ngesaziso kwabahilelekile ; 
Akukho lutho kule ngxenye okunqinda igunya lenkantolo lokuhlola ukuthi ukulimala kufakazelwe yini , nokuthi kuye kwahlawuliswa ngokwanele ; 
Uma isicelo sesifakiwe eNkantolo Yobulungisa ngokwemibandela yesigatshana , iNkantolo Yobulungisa ingase iyaleze ukuba udaba lwethulwe kuyo esikhundleni senkantolo yabathengi uma kuyoba lula futhi ubulungisa budinga ukuba kwenziwe kanjalo . 
Uma uKhomishane ekhipha isaziso sokungalidlulisi icala ngenxa yesikhalazo , ngaphandle ngokwezizathu ezichazwe esigabeni 116 , umfaki wesikhalazo okhathazekile angase adlulisele udaba ngokuqondile enkantolo yabathengi , uma ikhona , esifundazweni umfaki wesikhalazo ahlala kuso , noma lapho ummangalelwa aqhuba khona ibhizinisi lakhe eliyinhloko kwiRiphabhuliki , kuye ngokwesishaya-mthetho sesifundazwe esilawula ukusebenza kwenkantolo yabatheng ; 
futhi othintekayo oqondise le ndaba kummeleli wezezimboni olwa nenkohlakalo angase abe esefaka isikhalazo kuKhomishane ngokuvumelana nenqubo okubhekiselwe kuyo esigabeni 71 . 
Uma uKhomishane ethula udaba enkantolo yabathengi ngokwemibandela yengxenyana , noma ngubani othintekayo kulokho kwethulwa kodaba angase afake isicelo eNkantolo Yobulungisa , ngendlela ebhalwe phansi phakathi nesikhathi esinqunyiwe , ukuze acele isigunyazo sokuba udaba lwethulwe ezithebeni zeNkantolo Yobulungisa . 
noma uma udaba lungamthinti umphakeli ochazwe endimeni  aqondise lolu daba kummeleli wezezimboni onegunya elingokomthetho olwa nenkohlakalo , ogunyazwe ngokwemibandela yesigaba 82 , umphakeli engaphansi kwalowo mmeleli olwa nenkohlakalo ; 
