Uphenyo olwenziwa nguKhomishane  
Ukufaka isikhalo kuKhomishane  Noma yimuphi umuntu angase afake isikhalo maqondana nodaba oluchazwe esigabeni 69 , noma kuKhomishane ngendlela ebhalwe phansi , amangale ngokuthi umuntu uye wenza ngendlela engqubuzana nalo Mthetho . 
Uma umphakeli engakwazi ukudiliva lezo zimpahla ezichazwe esigatshaneni lapho umthengi esekhokhe imali ephelele ngalezo zimpahla , umphakeli kumelwe , ngokukhetha komthengi aphakele umthengi ngezimpahla ngesilinganiso esifanayo sobuningi bezimpahla ezifanayo noma zezinga eliphakeme , umklamo nekhwalithi ; 
futhi abuyise lezo zingxenye noma izakhi kumthengi entweni yokuphatha ehlanzeke ngokwamukelekayo ; 
