INQUBO YASEPHALAMENDE  
AMABALENGWE OMTHETHO-SIVIVINYO  
UMthetho-Sivivinyo ukhuthaza abaxabene ukuba bafune isisombululo sezingxabano zabo ngezinqubo zokuxazululwa kwezingxabano , ukubuyisana nokusetshenziswa kwabalamuli ezinkantolo zabo zabathengi ezisezinfundeni zabo , ama-Ombud namanye amanxusa . 
Kuyicala lobugebengu ukwehluleka ukwenza ngokuvumelana nomthetho . 
Isiqephu 2 soHlelo lwesibili , esiphathelene namalungiselelo oguquko , sihlinzeka ngohlelo lokulawula ukwethulwa koMthetho-Sivivinyo , ukuze abaphakel nabalawuli banikezwe isikhathi esanele sokulungisa izenzo nezinhlelo zabo ukuze bavumele ukusetshenziswa kwezimfuno ezintsha zalo Mthetho . 
Okudlulisela kuMshushisi Kazwelonke izindaba eziqondene namacala obugebengu ngokwemibandela yalo Mthetho . 
Abeluleki Bezomthetho Bombuso banomuzwa wokuthi akudingekile ukuba lo Mthetho-Sivivinyo udluliselwe eMkhandlwini Kazwelonke Wabaholi Bendabuko ngokwemibandela yesigaba 18 yoMthetho Wobuholi Bendabuko Nohlaka Lobubusi , ka-2003 , njengoba ungenazo izinhlinzeko eziphathelene nomthetho wamasiko noma amasiko emiphakathi yendabuko . 
Izijeziso zobugebengu ziqondene namacala obugebengu kanti izijeziso zobuqondisi ziphathelene nokuziphatha okwenqatshelwe . 
UMTHETHO WEZEZIMBONI  
Izinqumo zeNkantolo Yobulungisa zingakhalazelwa noma zihlolwe yiNkantolo Ephakeme . 
Kucatshangwa ukuthi imali engangezigidi ezingu-R51 ,3 kuzodingeka ibhajethelwe lokhu ngonyaa wezimali ka-2009/10 . 
Ukudlulisela izingxabano ezingaxazululwanga ezinkantolo zabathengi zesifundazwe . 
futhi aphenye bese ehlola ukuziphatha okwenqatshelwe okumangalelwe futhi aphoqelele ukuba kwenziwe ngokuvumelana nalo Mthetho . 
Okudlulisela eNkantolo Yobulungisa izindaba eziphathelene nokuziphatha okwenqatshelwe okumangalelwe ngokwemibandela yalo Mthetho . 
UKUPHOQELELWA KOMTHETHO  
Okokugcina , njengoba kuqashelwa ukuthi abanye omasipala kungenzeka babhekene nezithiyo zemithombo kanye namandla okuphakela okungase kunqinde amandla abo lokubhekela izibopho zabo ezintsha njengabaphakeli bezimpahla namasevisi kubathengi , imithetho yoguquko igunyaza uNgqongqoshe , ngesicelo sikaNgqongqoshe kaHulumeni Wasekhaya ukuba abambezele ngokuqhubekayo ukusetshenziswa kwemithetho ethile yoMthetho-Sisekelo kulabo masipala njengoba kungase kubonakale kudingekile . 
UMthetho-Sivivinyo uhlongoza ukuba kumiswe uKhomishane ozohlinzeka ngokuqondiswa okuphumelelayo kwalo Mthetho ebambisene neNkantolo Yobulungisa Yabathengi Kazwelone . 
Amagunya okuvikelwa kwabathengi esifundazwe angase futhi acele uKhomishane ukuba afake isikhalazo maqondana nanoma yikuphi ukuziphatha okwenqatshelwe noma ubugebengu ngokwemibandela yalo Mthetho . 
UMthetho-Sivivinyo uhlinzeka ngokukhishwa kwezijeziso zobugebengu nezobuqondisi . 
