IZINHLANGANO ZOKUQONDISA  
Lo Mthetho-Sisekelo unikeza uKhomishane amandla : Okukhipha isaziso sokuhlonipha umthetho kumuntu noma enhlanganweni yabantu leyo uKhomishane ngezizathu ezizwakalayo , akholelwa ukuthi iye yabandakanyeka ekuziphatheni okwenqatshelwe . 
enze ucwaningo futhi ahlongoze ukuba kwenziwe izinguquko ukuze kuthuthukiswe ukutholakala kalula kwemakethe yabathengi noma ukufinyelelwa kwemigomo yoMthetho ; 
Iminyango elandelayo iye yathintwa ngalo Mthetho-Sivivinyo : 
UMnyango Wezokuthutha  
UMnyango Wezezindlu  
UKhomishane Wabathengi Kazwelonke uzomiswa njengenxusa lombuso elinesibopho kuNgqongqoshe . 
Yonke iminyango yezezimali nezomnotho yezifundazwe  
Lo Mthethosivivinyo uphakamisa ukuthi iNhloko Yamajaji kufanele iqoke ithimba lamajaji elinolwazi oluvelele oluhambisana nalokhu ukuze akwazi ukwahlulela uma kubakhona ukungaboni ngaso linye okudalwa ukubuyiswa komhlaba ; 
Ngenxa yokuba khona kwezinqwaba zeziphathimandla ezikuhulumeni kazwelonke , ezifundazweni nakohulumeni basemakhaya ezinamandla okubuyisa umhlaba , kuba nesidingo sokuqinisekisa ukuthi kuba nendlela efanayo elandelwa yizikhungo zikahulumeni ukuqhuba ukubuyiswa komhlaba . 
Ekubhalweni kwawo lo Mthethosivivinywa , uMnyango waxhumana ngqo noMnyango Wezindaba Zemihlaba kanye noMnyango Wezobulungiswa kanye Nokuthuthukiswa koMthethosisekelo . 
INQUBO YEPHALAMENDE  
intengo yomhlaba ezimakethe ; 
kanye nenhloso yokuthathwa kwalowo mhlaba ; 
Iziphathimandla zokuthathwa komhlaba kufanele zibhekelele zonke izethulo futhi kufanele zizame ukufinyelela esivumelwaneni nalabo amalungelo kanye nezinzuzo zabo ezizothinteka kabi ngaphambi kokufika esinqumeni sokudla umhlaba ; 
Ngokwalo Mthetho , abanamalungelo abhalisiwe kuphela kanye namanye athile angabhalisiwe abanelungelo lokuthola isinxephezelo uma kuthathwa umhlaba kubo . 
iziphathimandla zokubuyiselwa umhlaba kanye nabo bonke abathintekayo , bacebisane ngolwazi olunzulu kanye neminye imininingwane ebalulekile ukuze bakwazi ukufinyelela esivumelwaneni sokutholakala kwesinxephezelo . 
NgoNovemba ka 2007 uMnyango Wezemisebenzi Yomphakathi washicilela uHlaka Lwenqubomgomo olumayelana noMthethosivivinywa Wokubuyiswa Komhlaba ukuze abantu baveze imibono yabo futhi kwathi ngoFebruwari ka 2008 , uMnyango nezinhlaka zikahulumeni kanye nezikhungo ezizimele bahlela izinkundla zokucobelelana ngalo Mthethosivivinywa . 
Uma kungafinyelelwa esivumelwaneni , iziphathimandla zokubuyiselwa umhlaba ziyobe sezenza isinqumo sokukhipha isinxephezelo . 
ABeluleki boMbuso kwezoMthetho kanye noMyango Wezemisebenzi Yomphakathi babona ukuthi lo Mthethosivivinywa kufanele uthathwe njengokulandela isigaba 75 soMthethosisekelo njengoba ungahlinzeki umgudu njengalokhu ubekiwe esigabeni se 74 noma se 76 kuMthethosisekelo . 
nanokuthi kucinywe uMthetho noMthetho Wezindaba Zemihlaba ka 1987 .Kodwa-ke uMkhandlu Wezindaba Zemihlaba okhona njengamanjd uzoqhubeka nokwenza umsebenzi wawo kuze kube kusungulwa uMkhandlu Kazwelonke Wokweluleka Ngokubuyiselwa Komhlaba . 
Le Mikhandlu iyophinde inikezele ngolwazi lokweluleka izinhlaka zikahulumeni mayelana nenani lalowo mhlaba okuyobe kubhekenwe nawo ngaleso sikhathi uma uhulumeni ekhetha ukuthenga umhlaba othile okanye ukuwudayisa . 
UMTHELELA KWEZEZIMALI KUHULUMENI  
Ngakho-ke kuyobe kuyaphambana noMthethosisekelo ukuqeda amalungelo angabhalisiwe ngaphandle kokukhipha isinxephezelo ; 
Kodwa-ke futhi uma omunye wabathintekayo engasamukeli isinqumo senkantolo , unelungelo lokudlulisa leso sinqumo , acele ukuba sibhekisiswe kabusha ; 
bonke abathintekayo baziswe ngokuthathwa komhlaba okuhlongozwayo , ukuze banikezwe ithuba lokukuphikisa lokhu futhi benze nezethulo kwiziphathimandla zokuthathwa komhlaba , ngaphambi kokuba isinqumo sokuhlwitha umhlaba sithathwe . 
Ishicilelwe ngabakwa Creda Communications . 
Lo Mthethosivivinywa uhlose ukwenza ukuthi lo Mthetho uhambisane noMthethosisekelo futhi unikeze izinhlaka zikahulumeni uhlaka olungumhlahlandlela kanye nemigudu nezindlela zokubuyiswa komhlaba , ngokuthi kuhlinzekelwe ukuthi kusatshalaliswe izinhloso ezingaholela ekubuyisweni komhlaba kususelwa kulokho okucatshangwa abantu ngokubuyiselwa umhlaba ukuze kufakwe phakathi ukubuyiswa komhlaba ngenhloso yokuthi kuzuze abantu . 
izimali eziyotshalwa nguhulumeni kanye nezimali ezingaba wuxhaso ngalowo mhlaba kanye nezimali zokuthuthukiswa kwalowo mhlaba ; 
kukhokhelwe izinxephezelo eziphusile nezifanele kulabo bantu abathintekayo ekuthathweni komhlaba , izinxephezelo ezinjalo-ke kuyofanele ukuthi zibonise ukubhekela lokho okufunwa abantu kanye nalokho okufunwa yilabo abathintekayo . 
kwenziwe futhi kugcinwe umqulu wazo zonke izakhiwo okanye umhlaba nguMnyango Wezemisebenzi Yomphakathi . 
Kodwa-ke uma ngabe umnikazi womhlaba othintekayo kumbe lowo onelungelo kulelo pulazi engathandi ukwamukela isinxephezelo , unelungelo lukufaka udaba enkantolo ukuze uhlelo lonke lubuyekezwe kabusha . 
