Yingakho zonke izithwalambiza zanamuhla zihlala imilenze yazo yangaphambili yemboze ubuso : zidumisa inyanga eyaxolela ukhokho wazo futhi yabuyisela nokubona kwakhe . 
Ngeke ngiyeke manje , kwasho isithwalambiza saqala sagibela . 
Mina , ngihlakaniphe kakhulu . 
